Clearing a line sets the background color (required by htop):
******************************[15D[42m[2K[m

Partial line clears:
******************************[10D[0K[10D[1K

CSI P (delete chars):
abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz[999P[20D[10P

CSI @ (insert blanks):
abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz[999@[20D[10@

CSI X (erase chars):
abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz[999X[20D[10X
